game -- rocket starts by taking off on the moon to fly from one level to the next

- there are deadly metors and other such obstacles
- as the levels progress, the harder it becomes
- there is falling (tbd fuel) you must collect
    - fuel Bar for the rocket
        - the less fuel, the slower it goes until it falls out of the screen
- the rocket moves by the flame boost (if no boost, it falls gradually)
- in the backround there is the level counter like the score counter in 'buckshot'
- when you reach a new highscore there is a line ingame showing that as you progress